    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains its composure with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, while the chassis remains rigid with documented subframe reinforcement. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment to ensure the high-pressure double-VANOS timing remains within factory tolerances. Riding on staggered Style 67 alloys, this M3 offers an authentic analog experience for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
