    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and daily practicality. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic paint that still retains a brilliant luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use, the body remains straight and free of any major dings. Step inside to a non-smoker cabin where the leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics\u2014including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has a full service history with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection performed just last month. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brake rotors were recently surfaced for smooth stopping power. This car drives straight, shifts seamlessly, and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any deferred maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 34500.0,
